						               													<description>Fruit Ninja: Slice &amp;amp; Dice is a strategic dice game for 2 to 4 players where each players are trying impress Sensei by slashing specific combos of Fruits.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round is splited in 2 phases:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Rolling Phase: Simultaneously and in real-time, all players have 20 seconds to roll up to 3 times their dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Buying Phase: In clock-wise order, starting from the first player, all players get a chance to spend their dice result on Combo Cards and claim one of the 6 Goal cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends as soon as the Combo Deck runs out. The winner is the one with the most points!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Kickstarter campaign was initiated for a series of 3 games based on the popular app game. Having not met the expected goals, the campaign was terminated. From the 3 games announced, only 1 made it to print: Fruit Ninja: Combo Party.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
